parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoWoCl.What are you doing? You startled me…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaEx.This is my secure storage location… But you have to leave; I’m expecting some company.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Jon… The police are on their way.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.Sorry, Jon. But if you’re not careful, in the next few minutes you could end up dead.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoAnOp.What the hell are you talking about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H2MaOp^.Hey! What the hell is he doing here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnDe^.Looks like the jig is up! The cops are onto us!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Let him go! You have no escape!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Make sure no one leaves this warehouse…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Come on, 1Hero. We can’t let them get away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.Bullshit! These are the kingpins and I’m the undercover agent who took them down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoAnOp>.Hey! I’m not a part of their gang.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OaAnDe^.You’re all going to jail for a long, long time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx.It’s hard to believe that the Eclipse Guild has been here in North Santiva.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlOp.It’s been a long case, that’s for sure. But nothing Nellie Cole couldn’t handle.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx^.I’m the lead detective on this case. We were lucky to be here thanks to an anonymous tip.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeHaCl.Not from me… It’s a total coincidence that the officers showed up when they did.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnEx^.1Hero! Say something. Women over 45 love you!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.What can I say? We took them down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx.Is there anyone left? Any other connections that you might want to mention?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx^.Charles Wilkes was their leader. Without him, they are falling apart.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeWoCl.Oh, shit… I had no idea that Wilkes was connected to this. What a funny coincidence!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx.Sounds like the Guild has been operating here a long time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnEx^.What the hell is wrong with you three? Give us something juicy!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.I have interrogations to attend to. I’ll spill every detail once I know more.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeHaEx.Yeah! Me too!... Nellie Cole has all the juicy details.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.Could be the rest of the day… into the night.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlFrEx^.Let me get some more b-roll and I’ll meet you back at Channel 4.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp.Do you have photos of the painting? Where is it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.We’ll give you everything tonight. Just be sure to run a teaser as soon as you can.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.We’re counting on you to get the word out as soon as possible.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.1Hero, I suggest you speak with the commissioner sooner rather than later.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeHaOp.Can I come to the station with you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeHaEx.Happy to serve the community of North Salvania!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaOp.Will the commissioner let you get behind the camera again?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I don’t know. She won't be happy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.In her eyes, we let all of them get away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx.Good luck, 1Hero. If you don’t get your job back, you know where you’re welcome.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OaAnEx.Go on, Canmore. You can’t hang around here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Dig deep, officer. Don’t let Duncan get away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OaAnEx.Go away, Canmore. You’re not a detective anymore.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OaAnEx.Go away, Canmore. You’re not a detective anymore.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OaAnEx.Go away, Canmore. You’re not a detective anymore.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp<.There’s something shiny in the wall, but I can’t reach it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe<.Is there a way to pull something shiny toward me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "You can now find this character profile in your album.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaEx.Packing up shop soon. Need to take tomorrow off for my court appearance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Been busy. Haven’t had a chance to talk to Commissioner Kimura… But she wants the Guild case dead… You might get lucky.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoFrEx.Well… The cops left the bunker and didn’t tape it off… I guess the crime scene investigation is over.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Don’t be surprised if we never speak of this case again.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Come on, Jon… It’s a stain on Kimura’s reputation.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoWoEx.Get the fingerprint locks to me soon, 1Hero. I have a lot of prep work to get done before tonight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoHaEx.This will work perfectly and just in time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.What are your plans for tomorrow, Jon? You’re going to court, right?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaDe.Play with fire long enough and I guess you’ll get burnt…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoFlEx.But I might just have a way out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I can something loose on the AC unit. I wonder if I could throw something at it and knock it down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.There’s something in this shipping container, but do I dare enter?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.You wouldn’t happen to have a crossbow, would you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaDe.Why a crossbow? Don’t you have a real gun?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaDe.I can get you a crossbow. Is that all?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I also need enough TNT to blow up a small building.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoWoDe.Now that’s not going to be easy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I also need a way to detonate it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaDe.What you need is a burner cell phone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.That’s not going to work… The bomb won't have reception where we’ll be putting it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaEx.I have a client that deals in road construction who has explosives… But I can’t just give you that much dynamite.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.No chance of accidentally losing his shipment?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaOp.Let’s make a deal. Put together the detonator, I’ll make the bomb and a crossbow…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaEx.In return, I need you to find me three handguns.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaEx.Not so fast. These handguns were tossed into the lake.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoFlEx.Find me the handguns and the bomb is yours.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Do I dare ask why you need these guns?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.We’re running short on time, but I’ll see what I can do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaEx.If you want a timebomb, bring me a detonator.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoFlEx.Give it to me and I’ll make you a timebomb.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.I’m in a hurry. How long will this take?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoWoEx.This is dangerous stuff, 1Hero. I can’t rush it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.I’ll come back later… But I need it today.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoMaExNo1>.I said get the hell out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoWoEx^.Careful, 1Hero! I don’t know what they put in there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I’m sure the cops cleared it out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McMaOp.You can’t hide! I’m coming after you, creep!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I know Jon. You can lay low here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.If it’s not too much of a burden.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoFlDeNo3.Haha. What kind of trouble are you all getting into?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.We’ve got some big problems at the mansion and I don’t trust that we’re safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoFlOp.No need to explain. I’ve got you covered.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnFrOp^.So what’s there to do around here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChAnEx^.We’re not here to have fun, Hannah.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoFlDe.I like the way the redhead thinks.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I’ve got to run. Take care of them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoFlEx.I’ve got your back, 1Hero. Your harem is safe with me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnHaAg.This place has a lot of cool stuff! I want to buy something!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFlOp.Don’t get yourself into too much trouble, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Everything’s okay… Father Solomon is at the mansion… keeping an eye on things.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnHaOp^.The priest is fighting monsters at the mansion?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaDe.I’m trying to stay out of your business, 1Hero, but something’s come up and I can’t look after your ladies anymore.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaEx.A new client. Emergency shipping is needed apparently and I have to start working on the order now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnSaDe^.I was just starting to like it here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.We’ll get out of your hair, Jon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.We’ll go back to the church. There are people there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.She’s not at the church. I brought her to the police station.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.We could all go there if you’d rather… But we have to lay low.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnSaEx^.I want to go back to the church and play in the woods.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaAnDe.You’ll be sticking close to me, young lady.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.The church is safe. If anything comes out of the rift, I’ll let you know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.It’s hard to explain… Everyone just stay away from the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaDe.I suspected a cult was forming there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaWoEx.You don’t have to tell me twice. The Lord protects us, but we also have to use our brains.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnHaEx^.Amen! Now let's go back so I can find my pet alligator.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaEx.1Hero, perhaps you can help me out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoWoEx.My client needs some high-tech security locks and I need them today.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaEx.The kind I need takes weeks to order. But perhaps you can do me this favor.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.How do I get a hold of them?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaEx.The police station. It’s the same system you use there for your door locks.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Are you sure? I don’t remember seeing any.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaEx.Not every door has it. But I know for a fact that it’s policy to keep extras on-hand.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I have no idea where they would be.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoBaEx.You’re my only hope, 1Hero. They are called fingerprint locks.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrDe.Well… You did watch the ladies for me…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoWoEx.Get them to me soon, 1Hero. I have a lot of prep work to get done before tonight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.I’m telling you, I can’t find him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFlEx^.But the pieces will still work, right?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.It’s hard to explain… Lilith took her body.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoEx^.There has to be a way to fix this! There’s always a way!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.He can… But they are not easy to keep track of… They can teleport.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoDe^.If you kill Lilith… what chance do we have of getting back Erica?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.… She claims she can save Erica.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Then stop whining and go find her!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElShEx^.1Hero… I get eight million more if I can find it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeBaEx.Let’s say we find it. Can we destroy it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.Those effects… they will work even if it’s in pieces.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I tried to break it… It didn’t work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFrEx^.Well… We can try harder next time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnEx.We couldn’t find anyone… Madalyn has more monsters for her army.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Lilith saved him… I don’t know where they are.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoEx.1Hero… There’s something you need to know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoEx.Madalyn stole something called a soul crystal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnEx^.She’s using it to store the soul of a powerful demon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoEx.I don’t know why. Madalyn had the soul inside of her… but she gave it up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.To allow Lilith to come to Earth.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaDe^.But why? She already had the soul of a demon. Why Lilith?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Because they share the same end goal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Madalyn came here specifically for Zephaniah… Together they opened the rift.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaDe^.Perhaps she needed Daemalius’ power to open it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaEx.And after they opened it… She used the crystal to keep his soul locked away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.What is this soul crystal you speak of? Where did it come from?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFlOp^.How much will you give me if I find that?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeWoEx.We need to get out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoEx.We can go back… But the cops are at the mansion too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElAnOp^.I’m not going to jail. I’ll die before I do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.There’s a way out… We can go to the church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Close the bunker, Jon. Don’t let those cops touch any of my treasure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.I have someone coming to pick me up…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I don’t know exactly. But the mansion is swarming with cops.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErHaOp.I can’t wait for our next adventure!");
